{"tid":2511253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"總統參選確認！美國前總統川普：我將會於2024參選！","createTime":"2021-04-30T18:38:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T02:45:40.000Z","uid":52658,"like":18,"dislike":84,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5f31ddb0f2ae34782f10fcafff9ccd0ba867b464","tid":2511253,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T18:38:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmS7mZxyspFSu7LoRtEXLBnqZEt2xxug6qNECaLoJcWQC7?filename=7ZNRcVc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ZNRcVc.png&h=49912339&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國前總統川普雖在2020大選敗給民主黨對手拜登，但他並不甘願離開白宮。川普最近受訪表示，「100%考慮2024出馬競選總統」。川普同時抨擊拜登政府對中國太慢採取行動，還說中國遲早有一天會接收美國。<br />\n<br />\n當主持人提問是否有意重新角逐白宮寶座時，川普不加思索地回說：「會。百分之百」（Yes, 100 percent.）他表示，民調顯示所有人都希望他回來當總統，所以「我百分之百會考慮出馬競選，而且我相信結果一定會成功」。<br />\n<br />\n哈佛大學美國政治研究中心與哈里斯民調（Harvard CAPS/Harris Poll）上月初的一項民調顯示，52%受訪共和黨員仍支持川普在2024角逐黨內提名，支持前副總統潘斯（Mike Pence）的共和黨員則只佔18%。<br />\n<br />\n川普還說，疫情爆發時若不是他當總統，「我們到現在都不會有疫苗」，他說：「從某方面來說，我是疫苗之父，因為是我推動這件事的。」<br />\n<br />\n疫苗之父<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你知唔知醜<br />\n拜登而家日日確診個案屢創新低<br />\n相反你條撚樣在任果陣每日十幾萬宗咁上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係你條柒碌 美國人洗撚打疫苗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你最自豪既中國牌<br />\n人地布林肯做得好過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n敗選就返去檢討下 美國人咁憎你到底係咩原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有 提提大家<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXUYKy4H8tTQSBMfgzMEucmSJwahyja4Nbww1GxqqLpo1?filename=YioAEAH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYioAEAH.png&h=2e1a6f03&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f9c43ab7fcab1ed911db2b426989c67467b1237c","tid":2511253,"uid":52658,"like":9,"dislike":8,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T18:45:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmagqdvPAmyeVbyBPsLcvkdq4v7hcYZEc2sre5Fk8SdP1c?filename=pyPPJ4K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpyPPJ4K.jpg&h=48c72ed5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7ae95772d717e8d601437c64bb4066ea06020b5","tid":2511253,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T18:50:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21caa9c9ee0934fa1a38fa1454f929f15dbe7ecb","tid":2511253,"uid":374660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T18:54:51.000Z","msg":"標題黨"},{"pid":"a142752cb4f36d83bc9b51170f26d902fbd3a0b1","tid":2511253,"uid":65289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T18:55:43.000Z","msg":"100% <span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">會考慮</span></span>"},{"pid":"cf8cecfb5f7d803d5a9fab9d8e4fff67ef90a22f","tid":2511253,"uid":89182,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T18:59:10.000Z","msg":"又想胶化愛侵力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f4695f1426fb2abfae47a370eb22d592f372daa","tid":2511253,"uid":373438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T19:01:33.000Z","msg":"2024前搞唔死佢先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b034bb3278632c08304b1ecba9a66351cddaa3bf","tid":2511253,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T19:47:56.000Z","msg":"原來Biden 未上台之前就可以控制美國政府投資藥廠買疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，定係樓豬覺得藥廠係今年一月Biden贏左之後先開始研發vaccine ？"},{"pid":"7986d5939a98246b9a48bae2ca663a841f957543","tid":2511253,"uid":50275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b034bb3278632c08304b1ec